NK013(pa)005:1601: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' bdag gis bsgrubs //
NK013(pa)005:1602: byang chub spyod dka' bdag gis spyad //
NK013(pa)005:1604: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK013(pa)005:1609: skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba dang bzhi las /
NK013(pa)005:1611: yang dag don gyi snying po ni //
NK013(pa)005:1612: ji snyed brjod pa'i kha brgyud kyang //
NK013(pa)005:1613: gang nas btsal kyang mi rnyed pas //
NK013(pa)005:1614: rang rig dri med dag pa yin //
NK013(pa)005:1615: de la rtag tu mos pa ni //
NK013(pa)005:1616: bsnyen pa'i dam pa mchog yin no //
NK013(pa)005:1617: sems nyid theg par rab nges na //
NK013(pa)005:1619: d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs pa //
NK013(pa)005:1620: da lta nyid du mngon gyur cig /
NK013(pa)005:1621: ces de kho na nyid kyi don dran pas nges shes bskyed do //
NK013(pa)005:1623: dbye gzhi'i dkyil 'khor legs par gsal btab nas /
NK013(pa)005:1624: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he phata dzah h+aum s+w+aa +aam h+aa phata dzah zhes brjod pas /
NK013(pa)005:1625: dam tshig gi 'khor lo las ye shes kyi dkyil
NK013(pa)005:1626: 'khor rten dang brten par bcas pa logs su phye
NK013(pa)005:1627: nas / mdun gyi nam mkhar me ri 'dab 'byar gyi tshul du bzhugs par mos pa'o //
NK013(pa)005:1629: bdag mdun gyi lha rnams kyi ye shes sems dpa'
NK013(pa)005:1630: so so'i thugs kar rang rang gi phyag mtshan gyi
NK013(pa)005:1631: lte bar dwangs ma'i srog h+aum yig la sogs pa'i
NK013(pa)005:1632: mthar bzla bya'i sngags kyi phreng bas bskor bar gsal
NK013(pa)005:1633: btab la / sngags zlos pa'i tshe /
NK013(pa)005:1634: bdag gi thugs ka nas sngags kyi 'od zer mchod
NK013(pa)005:1635: pa'i tshul du spros pas ye shes kyi lha tshogs
NK013(pa)005:1638: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs dang dngos grub thams
NK013(pa)005:1639: cad 'od dang 'od zer gyi rnam pas bdag la
NK013(pa)005:1640: stsal zhing thim par dmigs la /
NK013(pa)005:1641: dam ye 'phro 'du ste gsal ba gsum dang ldan pa'i dang nas /
NK013(pa)005:1654: h+aum la s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)005:1656: tram m+aa le sa ma ya hoh h+r+aim h+aa h+aum pad+ma pra da ma /
NK013(pa)005:1657: h+r+aim g+ai ti r+aa go ham /
NK013(pa)005:1659: a nirti r+aa ga ya mye /
NK013(pa)005:1660: mee d+h+aa ra na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)005:1662: th+l+him nis+sa ram b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)005:1664: h+aum swa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)005:1665: bam d+ai pa su gi r+ai /
NK013(pa)005:1666: m+aum sh+r+ai am r+aa ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)005:1668: h+aum ya m+aan+ta kri ta phata /
NK013(pa)005:1669: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h+aum phata /
NK013(pa)005:1671: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ro ma h+aa sogs /
NK013(pa)005:1673: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ro ma h+aa sogs /
NK013(pa)005:1675: ma h+aa ka rma d+ha ro ma h+aa sogs /
NK013(pa)005:1677: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta ah mu ne krem s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)005:1678: mu ne h+aum trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)005:1683: zhes pa rnams rim pa bzhin brgya dang nyer gcig
NK013(pa)005:1684: sogs gtso 'khor gyi 'gros dang sbyar nas bzlas zhing
NK013(pa)005:1686: rnam shes nam mkha' ma sogs kyi dzapa bskul yang bya bar bshad do //
NK013(pa)005:1688: rtags dang dus dang grangs kyi dbye bas rab 'bring
NK013(pa)005:1689: tha ma'i tshad rdzogs kyi bar du bya bar gsungs
NK013(pa)005:1690: kyang / mos sgom nyid chog sogs la ci nus tsam bzla ba yin no //
NK013(pa)005:1691: gzhan du mkha' khyab kyi spro bsdu'i bzlas pa nyid
NK013(pa)005:1692: mchog tu bshad pa yod kyang don gyi gnad gcig
NK013(pa)005:1693: go // bzhi pa skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba la /
NK013(pa)005:1696: ye shes pa bsdu ba dang gsum /
NK013(pa)005:1698: gzhi bstod bya bar gsungs pa ltar /
NK013(pa)005:1700: rnam shes rnam dag bcom ldan rdo rje sems //
NK013(pa)005:1701: zhe sdang rnam dag chos dbyings ye shes ngang //
NK013(pa)005:1702: mthing ga phyag na rdo rje bar ba bsnams //
NK013(pa)005:1703: thugs mchog rdo rje sems la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)005:1704: gzugs phung rnam dag bcom ldan rnam snang mdzad //
NK013(pa)005:1705: gti mug rnam dag me long ye shes ngang //
NK013(pa)005:1706: dung mdog phyag na 'khor lo 'bar ba bsnams //
NK013(pa)005:1707: sku mchog rnam snang mdzad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)005:1708: tshor ba rnam dag bcom ldan rin chen 'byung //
NK013(pa)005:1709: nga rgyal rnam dag mnyam nyid ye shes ngang //
NK013(pa)005:1710: gser mdog phyag na rin chen 'bar ba bsnams //
NK013(pa)005:1711: yon tan rin chen 'byung la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK013(pa)005:1713: / 'du shes rnam dag bcom ldan snang mtha' yas /
NK013(pa)005:1715: / 'dod chags rnam dag kun rtog ye shes ngang //
NK013(pa)005:1716: le brgan phyag na pad+ma 'bar ba bsnams //
NK013(pa)005:1717: gsung mchog snang mtha' yas la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK013(pa)005:1719: / 'du byed rnam dag bcom ldan don yod grub //
NK013(pa)005:1720: phrag dog rnam dag bya grub ye shes ngang //
NK013(pa)005:1721: ljang gu phyag na ral gri 'bar ba bsnams //
NK013(pa)005:1722: phrin las don yod grub la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK013(pa)005:1724: / 'byung ba rnam dag rigs kyi yum chen lnga //
NK013(pa)005:1725: kun bzang spyan ma m+aa ma gos dkar sgrol //
NK013(pa)005:1726: thabs kyi sku la shes rab dgyes 'khril ma //
NK013(pa)005:1727: rigs kyi yum chen lnga la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)005:1728: bskal bzang byang chub sems dpa' brgyad rnams ni //
NK013(pa)005:1729: bde bar gshegs pa kun gyi sras mchog ste //
NK013(pa)005:1730: yon tan mi zad sprul pa bsam yas pa'i //
NK013(pa)005:1731: sems dpa' chen po brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)005:1732: sgeg mo phreng thogs rin chen glu gar can //
NK013(pa)005:1733: bdug pa me tog mar me dri chab ma //
NK013(pa)005:1734: rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams la mchod 'bul ma //
NK013(pa)005:1735: mchod pa'i lha mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)005:1736: ye shes sgo ba chen po yab yum brgyad //
NK013(pa)005:1737: gshin rje stobs chen rta mgrin bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK013(pa)005:1738: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu ma //
NK013(pa)005:1739: sgo ba yab yum brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)005:1740: chos nyid stong pa'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK013(pa)005:1741: chos nyid kun tu bzang po 'du bral med //
NK013(pa)005:1742: chos nyid khyab brdal chen po'i ye shes kyis //
NK013(pa)005:1743: kun bzang yab yum gnyis la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)005:1744: ye shes bzhi las rigs bzhi'i phrin las kyis /
NK013(pa)005:1746: / 'jig rten drug gi bye ba phrag brgya ru //
NK013(pa)005:1747: sprul pa bye ba phrag brgyas 'gro drug gi //
NK013(pa)005:1748: don mdzad thub pa drug la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)005:1749: rgyal ba sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi //
NK013(pa)005:1750: che ba'i yon tan brjod kyi mi lang yang //
NK013(pa)005:1751: yon tan cha shas brjod pa'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK013(pa)005:1752: rig 'dzin sngags 'chang rnal 'byor bdag cag gi //
NK013(pa)005:1753: las dang nyon mongs bag chags gtan sbyangs nas //
NK013(pa)005:1754: tshe 'di nyid la rig 'dzin sa thob ste //
NK013(pa)005:1755: dpal ldan rdo rje sems dpa'i gnas thob shog /
NK013(pa)005:1758: ye nas gnyis med chos skur dag pa las //
NK013(pa)005:1759: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK013(pa)005:1760: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK013(pa)005:1761: de ldog don phyir rgyal ba'i dam mnos te //
NK013(pa)005:1762: bdag cag ma rig lus dang da ga sems kyis //
NK013(pa)005:1763: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur pas //
NK013(pa)005:1764: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK013(pa)005:1765: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK013(pa)005:1766: zhes bzlas pa'i nyes byas su gyur pa thams cad bshags shing dag par bya'o //
NK013(pa)005:1768: rang bzhin dang ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gnyis rang bzhin dbyer med du rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK013(pa)005:1769: badz+ra sa ma ya sogs lnga dang //
NK013(pa)005:1770: ye shes rgyal po sogs kyis rig pa'i me tog dor zhing dngos grub bskul nas /
NK013(pa)005:1773: ye shes kyi 'khor lo dam tshig pa la chu la chu bzhag pa bzhin dbyer med du thim /
NK013(pa)005:1776: badz+ra sa ma ya hoh zhes dbang du gyur nas dgyes shing chags par byas /
NK013(pa)005:1777: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis brtan cing gsal bar byas nas yi ge brgya pa'ang bazla'o //
NK013(pa)005:1778: gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga la /
NK013(pa)005:1783: spyod lam gyi rnal 'byor dang lnga /
NK013(pa)005:1784: dang po tshogs mchod la lnga las /
NK013(pa)005:1785: dang po bsham zhing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK013(pa)005:1786: dza gad dang m+aam sa gtso bor gyur pa'i yo byad ci 'byor ba bshams nas /
NK013(pa)005:1788: ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ais bsang /
NK013(pa)005:1789: ram yam kham gis bsreg gtor bkrus te stong par sbyang /
NK013(pa)005:1791: zhal zas kyi snod du nyi ma la h+aum s+w+aa
NK013(pa)005:1792: +aam h+aa las bza' btung gi dngos po ye shes
NK013(pa)005:1793: lnga'i rang bzhin bdud rtsi ro brgya pa 'dod yon
NK013(pa)005:1794: gyi rnam pa ma tshang ba med pa so so'i
NK013(pa)005:1795: lha mo'i rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang
NK013(pa)005:1796: bcas pa'i sprin 'phro bar bsam la /
NK013(pa)005:1797: yi ge gsum lan gsum brjod pas byin gyis brlabs /
NK013(pa)005:1798: gnyis pa tshogs zhing spyan 'dren pa ni //
NK013(pa)005:1799: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK013(pa)005:1800: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK013(pa)005:1802: tshogs mchog dkyil 'khor gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)005:1803: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' nyid //
NK013(pa)005:1804: rigs bzhi'i lha dang lha mo dang /
NK013(pa)005:1806: / 'khor gyi sems dpa' sems ma dang //
NK013(pa)005:1807: kun bzang sprul pa'i tshogs chen dang //
NK013(pa)005:1808: sgo ba bzhi sogs gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)005:1809: e h+ye hi sogs kyis tshogs zhing dpag tu med pa mkha' khyab tu sad par byas la //
NK013(pa)005:1810: thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK013(pa)005:1812: sh+r+ai badz+ra amng+ku sha dzah de bzhin du /
NK013(pa)005:1815: g+han+de hohs dgug gzhug bcing mnyes bya /
NK013(pa)005:1816: gsum pa mchod pa la gnyis kyi /
NK013(pa)005:1817: dang po ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)005:1819: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa mo //
NK013(pa)005:1821: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK013(pa)005:1824: rdo rje sgeg mo rdo rje can //
NK013(pa)005:1825: sems dpa' sngon po'i ye shes 'bebs //
NK013(pa)005:1826: me long lta bu'i ye shes las //
NK013(pa)005:1827: badz+ra l+aa s+ye'i mchod pa rol //
NK013(pa)005:1828: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga l+aa s+ye h+aum /
NK013(pa)005:1832: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes las //
NK013(pa)005:1833: badz+ra m+aa le'i mchod pa rol //
NK013(pa)005:1835: pad+ma dbyangs mkhan rma bya'i mgrin //
NK013(pa)005:1836: spyan ras gzigs kyi dngos grub 'dzin //
NK013(pa)005:1837: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes las //
NK013(pa)005:1839: g+ai ti h+r+aih gar mkhan 'gying bag gzi ldan ma //
NK013(pa)005:1841: bya ba nan tan badz+ra n+airti'i n+airti a /
NK013(pa)005:1843: gnyis pa tshogs rdzas kyi mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)005:1844: zhal zas kyi phud rim par spros la /
NK013(pa)005:1846: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur cing //
NK013(pa)005:1847: byang chub sems dang ma chags pa'i //
NK013(pa)005:1848: gnyis su med par thim gyur nas //
NK013(pa)005:1849: tshogs chen gnyis kyang rdzogs par rol /
NK013(pa)005:1851: / 'dod yon lnga po thams cad dang //
NK013(pa)005:1852: sna tshogs snang ba thams cad kun //
NK013(pa)005:1853: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK013(pa)005:1854: gzugs mdzes lha dang lha mor brtag /
NK013(pa)005:1855: sna tshogs gzugs ni thams cad kun //
NK013(pa)005:1856: snang stong ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK013(pa)005:1857: chos dbyings dag pa'i ye shes te //
NK013(pa)005:1858: rdo rje lha mo gzugs mdzes ma /
NK013(pa)005:1860: / 'dod yon phyag na bsnams nas ni //
NK013(pa)005:1861: rkang pas stabs byed lag gar bsgyur //
NK013(pa)005:1862: snyan pa'i glu dbyangs blangs nas ni //
NK013(pa)005:1864: thams cad ma lus sgra rnams ni //
NK013(pa)005:1865: grags stong ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK013(pa)005:1866: me long lta bu'i ye shes te //
NK013(pa)005:1867: rdo rje lha mo 'jam pa'i sgra /
NK013(pa)005:1870: bde ba tshim byed bsod nams te //
NK013(pa)005:1871: tshim stong ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK013(pa)005:1872: brjod med mi gnas ye shes te //
NK013(pa)005:1873: rdo rje chags med pad+ma'i gsung /
NK013(pa)005:1876: bde gshegs dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK013(pa)005:1877: bde ba ro yis tshim byed pa //
NK013(pa)005:1878: ro stong ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK013(pa)005:1879: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes te //
NK013(pa)005:1880: thams cad tshim byed ro yi lha /
NK013(pa)005:1883: rdo rje reg bya myong byed ma //
NK013(pa)005:1884: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK013(pa)005:1885: bde mchog dkyil 'khor yangs byed ma //
NK013(pa)005:1886: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes te //
NK013(pa)005:1887: rdo rje reg bya'i lha mo ni /
NK013(pa)005:1890: hoh bde bar gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs
NK013(pa)005:1891: rnams la tshogs kyi mchod pa chen po 'bul zhing
NK013(pa)005:1892: mchis na / sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes shing tshim nas //
NK013(pa)005:1893: dam tshig nyams chags thams cad skongs te /
NK013(pa)005:1894: bla na med pa'i dngos grub dam pa thob par mdzad du gsol /
NK013(pa)005:1896: su ra to bcu drug la sogs pa'i glu gar dang rol mo sna tshogs pas mchod nas /
NK013(pa)005:1897: bzhi pa tshogs la rol ba ni /
NK013(pa)005:1898: las kyi rdo rjes 'khor lo 'dus pa'i gtso bo
NK013(pa)005:1899: la phyag byas thabs shes kyi rdzas bsnol mar dbul
NK013(pa)005:1900: zhing / mnyam nyid mi g.yo mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas dpal //
NK013(pa)005:1901: log rtog mtshan ma'i spros pa ngang gis zhi //
NK013(pa)005:1902: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder spyad nas kyang //
NK013(pa)005:1903: mnyam rdzogs chen po'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)005:1905: des kyang pad+ma'i phyag rgya bskor zhing /
NK013(pa)005:1906: a la la hoh zhes blang /
NK013(pa)005:1907: de nas gzhan rnams la'ang rim par stob /
NK013(pa)005:1908: rnal 'byor pa rnams lha'i ting nge 'dzin gsal ba las /
NK013(pa)005:1909: khyad par dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyang rang gi
NK013(pa)005:1910: phung po dang khams dang skye mched nyid las mi
NK013(pa)005:1911: gnyis par shes pas nang gi sreg blugs kyi cho
NK013(pa)005:1912: ga ji lta ba'i dam tshig gis tshim par rol
NK013(pa)005:1915: hoh bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam
NK013(pa)005:1916: dral rnams kyis dza gad dpa' bo gsol bas 'gro
NK013(pa)005:1917: ba ma lus pa dbang du 'du bar gyur cig
NK013(pa)005:1918: / ma h+aa m+aam sa gsol bas rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen por gyur cig /
NK013(pa)005:1919: rdo rje'i tshe gsol bas rdo rje sems dpa'i tshe dang lang tsho la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK013(pa)005:1920: zhal zas kyi bye brag mang po gsol bas zhi
NK013(pa)005:1921: khro'i phrin las kyi rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs la dbang
NK013(pa)005:1924: lnga pa lhag ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)005:1925: lhag ma rnams gsog 'jog med par bsdus /
NK013(pa)005:1926: lha mchod pa'i lhag mas bsnan pa dkyil 'khor dang
NK013(pa)005:1927: ha cang mi nye ba'i shar lhor dri'i man+dala zlum
NK013(pa)005:1928: por byas pa'i steng du bzhag /
NK013(pa)005:1929: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba las khyad par lhag ma'i gnas su /
NK013(pa)005:1930: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK013(pa)005:1931: lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor mtshan nyid rdzogs pa gdan dang bcas pa'i nang gi dbus dang phyogs bzhir /
NK013(pa)005:1937: rigs kyi yab lnga skad cig gis gsal bar gyur /
NK013(pa)005:1938: gtor ma dam tshig gsang ba'i longs spyod 'dod yon
NK013(pa)005:1939: gyi phung po zad mi shes pas nam mkha' gang
NK013(pa)005:1940: bar bsam la / +aahh+aum lan gsum du brjod pas byin gyis brlabs te /
NK013(pa)005:1942: las kyi rdo rje byed par dbang bskur ba'i //
NK013(pa)005:1943: mkha' 'gro lhag sdug ma sring ging gi tshogs //
NK013(pa)005:1944: lhag ma kha chu'i dam la gtogs pa rnams //
NK013(pa)005:1945: dam tshig bzhin du mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)005:1946: hoh mkha' 'gro ma gsang ba'i rgyud du gtogs pa'i
NK013(pa)005:1947: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis sngon gyi thugs dam
NK013(pa)005:1948: dus las mi 'da' bar sgrub pa'i stong grogs la
NK013(pa)005:1949: gshegs shig / e +aa ra li h+r+aim h+r+aim dzahmh'u
NK013(pa)005:1950: bam hoh d+aa ki ni h'u dzah zhes brjod cing
NK013(pa)005:1951: he ru ka'i dam rgya dpral bar bcings nas spyugs
NK013(pa)005:1952: pa'i brda dang bcas pas spyan drangs pas mkha' 'gro
NK013(pa)005:1953: ma so gnyis sprin gtibs pa bzhin byon te /
NK013(pa)005:1954: rigs lnga'i gtso bo la gtso mo bdun /
NK013(pa)005:1956: gzhan gsum la lnga lnga 'khril zhing sgo ma bzhi gtso ba'i gdan gyi tshul du bzhugs pa la /
NK013(pa)005:1957: me tog la sogs pas spyir mchod nas /
NK013(pa)005:1958: dmar gyi rak+ta gtor ma la sbreng zhing /
NK013(pa)005:1959: he ru ka'i thod pa'i thal mo'i rgya dang bcas pas /
NK013(pa)005:1960: badz+ra d+aa ki n+ai pra t+aits+tshe mam ba lim ta h'u phata /
NK013(pa)005:1962: bud+d+ha d+aa ki n+ai sogs nas /
NK013(pa)005:1964: rat+na d+aa ki n+ai t+r+aam phata /
NK013(pa)005:1965: pad+ma d+aa ki n+ai h+r+aih phata /
NK013(pa)005:1967: ces pa gtor ma phul la /
NK013(pa)005:1969: rnam dag chos dbyings zhi ba las //
NK013(pa)005:1970: thugs rje chen po'i sprul pa 'byung //
NK013(pa)005:1971: rang rang las kyis bskul 'gyur bas //
NK013(pa)005:1972: sprul pa bsam yas mkha' la 'gro /
NK013(pa)005:1975: mi ro skam po'i gdan steng na //
NK013(pa)005:1976: thugs rjes sprul pa cir yang ston //
NK013(pa)005:1977: mthing ga mi bskyod la sogs gzugs //
NK013(pa)005:1978: sum cu rtsa gnyis kun 'dzin cing //
NK013(pa)005:1979: mi thod khrag gis bkang ba dang //
NK013(pa)005:1980: kha t+w+aam tri shul gshol gri bsnams //
NK013(pa)005:1981: rang rang lag cha sna tshogs ldan //
NK013(pa)005:1982: dpa' bo'i gzugs can kha mig bgrad //
NK013(pa)005:1983: nyi zla'i tshul du mkha' la 'gro //
NK013(pa)005:1984: zas su sha dang khrag dang ni //
NK013(pa)005:1985: khrag dang tshil bu rgyu ma za //
NK013(pa)005:1986: yang dag nyid de 'jig rten nyid //
NK013(pa)005:1987: sprul pa'i tshul gyis gzugs las sprul //
NK013(pa)005:1988: mkha' 'gro ma mo khyod rnams kyang //
NK013(pa)005:1989: sngon tshe bcom ldan rigs lnga la //
NK013(pa)005:1990: ye shes dbyings la chags tshul du /
NK013(pa)005:1992: / 'khril zhing rigs lnga'i slas su byas //
NK013(pa)005:1993: bstan pa bsrung bar mna' bor ba'i //
NK013(pa)005:1994: khas blangs 'gal bar mi bya'i phyir //
NK013(pa)005:1995: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK013(pa)005:1998: mkha' 'gro ging dang dbang phyug ma //
NK013(pa)005:1999: ma bdun sring bzhi 'bar ma brgyad //
NK013(pa)005:2000: pho nya la sogs lhag sdud tshogs //
NK013(pa)005:2001: dpal gyi pham phabs 'di gsol la //
NK013(pa)005:2002: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK013(pa)005:2003: ces brjod cing sman dang rak+tasa kyang mchod nas /
NK013(pa)005:2004: hoh lhag sdud kyi dam tshig la gtogs pa'i mkha'
NK013(pa)005:2005: 'gro dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa
NK013(pa)005:2006: rnams lhag ma'i dam tshig 'dis tshim zhing dgyes par
NK013(pa)005:2007: gyur te / dam tshig nyams chag thams cad skongs nas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs /
NK013(pa)005:2009: dge 'dun dang chos kyi rgyal srid skyongs /
NK013(pa)005:2011: sems can gyi phan bde spel /
NK013(pa)005:2012: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi stong grogs mdzod /
NK013(pa)005:2013: sngags 'chang rnams kyi phrin las sgrubs /
NK013(pa)005:2014: khyad par dam tshig 'dir 'dus pa rnams kyi phyi nang gsang ba'i 'gal rkyen zhi ba dang /
NK013(pa)005:2015: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa myur du 'grub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK013(pa)005:2018: mgron rnams rang gnas su gshegs par bsam la /
NK013(pa)005:2019: gtor ma phyi rol du bskyal /
NK013(pa)005:2020: h'u zhes pas lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi rigs lnga rang la bstim nas /
NK013(pa)005:2022: gnyis pa brtan ma bskyang ba ni /
NK013(pa)005:2023: phyi rol du brtan ma'i gtor ma sman phud kyi bran la /
NK013(pa)005:2024: tram s+pha sam tram rat+na tre lo kya phata /
NK013(pa)005:2025: gtor ma'i rdul phra rab re re zhing rin po
NK013(pa)005:2026: che'i gur khang longs spyod zad mi shes pas nam
NK013(pa)005:2030: tshogs dang bka' yi tshogs bcas nyid //
NK013(pa)005:2031: khrag 'thung de bzhin nam mkha'i sku //
NK013(pa)005:2032: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs skyong ma rnams /
NK013(pa)005:2034: / 'dir spyon dam skongs phrin las mdzod //
NK013(pa)005:2035: bdag nyid chen mo la sogs bdud mo bzhi //
NK013(pa)005:2036: gangs dkar sha med la sogs gnod sbyin bzhi //
NK013(pa)005:2037: kong btsun de mo la sogs sman mo bzhi //
NK013(pa)005:2038: bod khams skyong ba'i che zhe chen mo rnams //
NK013(pa)005:2039: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas //
NK013(pa)005:2040: lhab lhub mang po'i rgyan dang bcas //
NK013(pa)005:2041: sil snyan mang po'i sgra dang bcas /
NK013(pa)005:2043: / 'dir spyon dam skongs phrin las mdzod //
NK013(pa)005:2044: che zhe chen mo khyod rnams kyang //
NK013(pa)005:2045: a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK013(pa)005:2047: rlangs chen dpal gyi seng ge yis //
NK013(pa)005:2048: zhing chen stan la bkod nas kyang //
NK013(pa)005:2049: lag tu rdo rje gtad nas ni //
NK013(pa)005:2050: dbang bskur gsang ba'i mtshan nas brjod //
NK013(pa)005:2051: rdo rje 'chang gi gral du bzhag /
NK013(pa)005:2052: bod khams bsrung zhing skyong ba dang //
NK013(pa)005:2053: rnal 'byor sgrub pa'i grogs bya zhes //
NK013(pa)005:2054: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK013(pa)005:2055: g.yar dam gnyan po rjes dgongs la //
NK013(pa)005:2056: dam rdzas bka' yi gtor ma longs //
NK013(pa)005:2057: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK013(pa)005:2063: ma ma sring 'gro ma h'u b+h+yo h'u h'u /
NK013(pa)005:2065: ma h+aa pany+tsa sogs kyi sman raka sbreng /
NK013(pa)005:2067: ya hi gats+tshasa gshegs gsol byas la /
NK013(pa)005:2068: gtor ma gtsang sar bskyal lo //
NK013(pa)005:2069: gsum pa nyer bsdu bya ba ni /
NK013(pa)005:2070: thun mtshams la 'jug pa'am nyal ba na /
NK013(pa)005:2071: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he h'u s+w+aa +aam h+aa /
NK013(pa)005:2072: zhes pas dkyil 'khor gsal btab la /
NK013(pa)005:2073: badz+ra pad+ma sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)005:2074: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa ga ham /
NK013(pa)005:2075: a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK013(pa)005:2076: dzahh+aum bam hoh bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK013(pa)005:2078: yab yum snyoms par 'jug pa'i sbyor mtshams nas byang
NK013(pa)005:2079: chub sems kyi 'od zer gyi sprin 'phros pas snod
NK013(pa)005:2080: bcud thams cad dag cing 'od gsal bar byas /
NK013(pa)005:2083: dag pa'i snod bcud thams cad gzhal yas khang srung 'khor dang bcas pa la thim /
NK013(pa)005:2084: gzhal yas khang gi rgyan thams cad yab rnams la thim /
NK013(pa)005:2085: dngos po thams cad yum rnams la /
NK013(pa)005:2086: lha yab thams cad gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' la /
NK013(pa)005:2087: yum thams cad dbyings phyug ma la /
NK013(pa)005:2089: de ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK013(pa)005:2090: de ting nge 'dzin sems dpa' la /
NK013(pa)005:2092: h'u gyen rdzogs n+aa da'i bar du thim nas rnam
NK013(pa)005:2093: par rtog med lhun grub nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang
NK013(pa)005:2095: nyal ba las langs pa'am spyod lam la 'jug pa na /
NK013(pa)005:2098: rdo rje sems dpa' zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa snang stong sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i skur ldang ngo //
NK013(pa)005:2099: bzhi pa go cha bgo zhing lus bsrung ba ni /
NK013(pa)005:2100: rang nyid rdor sems su gsal ba'i spyi bor /
NK013(pa)005:2101: mgrin par +aah snying gar h'u yig rnams kyis mtshan par gyur /
NK013(pa)005:2102: badz+ra k+aa wa tsi rak+sha ham /
NK013(pa)005:2104: lus thams cad rdo rje rgya gram gyi go chas
NK013(pa)005:2105: zhu lugs su g.yogs pas sgo gsum rdo rje gsum
NK013(pa)005:2106: dang dbyer med du bcings par bltas la /
NK013(pa)005:2107: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs /
NK013(pa)005:2108: sku gsung thugs kyis kun la khyab //
NK013(pa)005:2109: ces brjod cing nga rgyal bya /
NK013(pa)005:2110: de nas mdzub mo g.yas su tram las khro bo
NK013(pa)005:2111: rdo rje gnod sbyin nag po phyag gnyis kyis mche
NK013(pa)005:2113: g.yon du las khro bo mi 'chi thab sbyor dmar
NK013(pa)005:2114: po rgya gram dang sdigs mdzub can du bskyed la
NK013(pa)005:2115: / lte ba snying ga ltag pa dang /
NK013(pa)005:2116: dpral ba spyi bo gnas lnga ru /
NK013(pa)005:2118: zhes brjod bzhin par 'dzub mo gnyis bsnol nas rim par reg pas /
NK013(pa)005:2119: gnas de dang der khro bo gnyis po zung re
NK013(pa)005:2120: zhabs bsnol nas zhal phyir gzigs te bsrung ba'i las
NK013(pa)005:2121: mdzad pa'i thugs ka nas rdo rje'i lu gu rgyud
NK013(pa)005:2122: byung bas bsrungs shing brtan par byas la /
NK013(pa)005:2123: rat+na mu ku ta a b+hi shiny+tsa tram tram /
NK013(pa)005:2124: zhes rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan gyis dbang bskur bar mos /
NK013(pa)005:2125: rat+na m+aa le a b+hi shiny+tsa tram tram /
NK013(pa)005:2126: rin po che'i phreng ba bcings par bsam mo //
NK013(pa)005:2127: +aar+ya lam+b+ho d+ha ra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aihh+r+aih dar mthing dmar gyi cod pan gyis brgyan par bsam mo //
NK013(pa)005:2128: gu h+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)005:2130: yi ge brgya pa lan gsum la sogs par bzlas pas shin tu brtan par byas la /
NK013(pa)005:2131: dge ba bsngo zhing bkra shis brjod pa rnams kyis mtha' rgyas par bya'o //
NK013(pa)005:2132: lnga pa spyod lam rgyun gyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK013(pa)005:2133: snod thams cad gzhal yas khang dang /
NK013(pa)005:2134: bcud thams cad rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK013(pa)005:2135: ba'i rang bzhin du yongs su shes pas spyod lam
NK013(pa)005:2137: rang gi rtsa dbu ma'i nang du thig le yungs
NK013(pa)005:2138: 'bru tsam pa gsal zhing 'tsher ba me stag phus
NK013(pa)005:2140: yang na sngar bshad pa'i nyer bsdu'i snying ga'i h'u
NK013(pa)005:2141: yig n+aa da'i bar du bsdus pa de nyid thig
NK013(pa)005:2142: le phra mo gsal zhing 'bar bar gyur pa la
NK013(pa)005:2144: des ni mi rtog pa'i ye shes rgyud la skye bar 'gyur ro //
NK013(pa)005:2146: bza' btung la tha mal pa'i gtsang zhen spangs nas sbyangs rtogs spar bas bdud rtsir byas la /
NK013(pa)005:2148: zhal gyi hom khung du phul ba gtum mo'i mes
NK013(pa)005:2149: bzhu ba'i dwangs ma'i bdud rtsi snying gar ye shes
NK013(pa)005:2150: sems dpa' sreg lha'i tshul du bzhugs pa'i zhal du
NK013(pa)005:2151: drangs par bsam la rol pa ni nang gi sbyin
NK013(pa)005:2152: sreg dang / sreg pa'i snyigs ma thal bar gyur
NK013(pa)005:2153: pa phyir sbyangs par bsam la rlung ro bsal bas
NK013(pa)005:2154: nad dang dug la sogs pas mi tshugs par bshad
NK013(pa)005:2155: sreg dang / do // spyi don gsum pa grub pa 'bras bu'i tshul la /
NK013(pa)005:2157: des grub pa'i tshad bstan pa las /
NK013(pa)005:2159: de ltar bshad pa'i rim pas thun bzhi la sogs
NK013(pa)005:2160: pas thun gyi ngo bo dang thun mtshams kyi rnal
NK013(pa)005:2161: 'byor thams cad la chos thams cad rang bzhin med
NK013(pa)005:2162: par shes pa'i lta ba dang /
NK013(pa)005:2163: rtsal snang dag pa rab 'byams sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK013(pa)005:2164: lam khyer dang ma bral ba la bslab par bya'o
NK013(pa)005:2166: tshul de lta bus rim par bsgoms pas rdzogs rim
NK013(pa)005:2167: gyi rtogs pa skye bar 'gyur ba'i rgyud smin par
NK013(pa)005:2168: 'gyur ba dang / de las rdzogs pa'i rim pa la byang chub par 'gyur zhing /
NK013(pa)005:2173: mthar phyin pa'i nyams dang lnga'i gnas skabs rnams smig
NK013(pa)005:2174: sgyu la sogs pa'i dpe lngas mtshon par gtan la
NK013(pa)005:2175: phebs shing / mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub
NK013(pa)005:2176: rnam pa gnyis po dka' ba med par myur du
NK013(pa)005:2181: d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs pa //
NK013(pa)005:2182: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK013(pa)005:2187: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel zhing //
NK013(pa)005:2188: longs spyod 'byung zhing ngan song sbyong //
NK013(pa)005:2190: nam mkha' rdo rje sra 'byung zhing /
NK013(pa)005:2196: thams cad stongs shing ltung bar 'gyur //
NK013(pa)005:2197: dgug dang btang dang bcing dang dgrol //
NK013(pa)005:2198: gso dang gsad dang pham dang rgyal //
NK013(pa)005:2200: zhes ji ltar gsungs pa bzhin 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK013(pa)005:2201: shin tu rmad byung gsang ba mchog gi gnas //
NK013(pa)005:2202: snying po'i mthar thug rdo rje sems dpa' che //
NK013(pa)005:2203: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zab dang rgya che'i mdzod //
NK013(pa)005:2204: rdo rje 'dzin dbang kun gyi 'jug ngogs yin //
NK013(pa)005:2205: de yi dkyil 'khor bde chen mchog gi gzhir //
NK013(pa)005:2206: myur bder bgrod byed rnal 'byor bskyed pa'i rim //
NK013(pa)005:2207: rab gsal sgrub pa'i thabs tshul bla na med //
NK013(pa)005:2208: ye shes char du 'bebs pa'i dngos grub dpyid /
NK013(pa)005:2211: rtag tu mnar zhing thabs bral ma gyur 'gro //
NK013(pa)005:2212: thabs mchog sku gsum lam gyi de nyid don //
NK013(pa)005:2213: ji bzhin 'char bar byed pa'i rgyur gyur cig /
NK013(pa)005:2214: bdag blo dman cing gzhung don rtogs dka' bas //
NK013(pa)005:2215: nongs par gyur gang rdo rje can la bshags //
NK013(pa)005:2216: dge ba 'di dang dus gsum bsags yod kun //
NK013(pa)005:2217: gsang chen bstan pa rgyas pa'i rgyur gyur cig /
NK013(pa)005:2218: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhi
NK013(pa)005:2219: ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi sgrub thabs ye shes
NK013(pa)005:2221: don gnyer can du mas yang dang yang du bskul ba dang /
NK013(pa)005:2222: rang gzhan mang po la phan pa'i ched du sgyu
NK013(pa)005:2223: 'phrul rtsa bshad kyi rgyud dang rgya gzhung rnams dang
NK013(pa)005:2224: / dpal ldan zur pa'i bshad sgrub kyi phyag bzhes
NK013(pa)005:2225: ji lta ba bzhin du gsang bdag chen po phrin
NK013(pa)005:2226: las lhun grub kyi bka' drin gyis 'tsho ba'i rig
NK013(pa)005:2227: pa 'dzin pa 'gyur med rdo rjes rab myos kyi
NK013(pa)005:2228: lo khrums kyi nya ba'i yar tshes dge ba la
NK013(pa)005:2229: o rgyan smin grol gling nges pa don gyi dga'
NK013(pa)005:2230: ba'i tshal chen po'i bla brang chos 'khor lhun por
NK013(pa)005:2231: sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni mkhas btsun bzang po'i
NK013(pa)005:2232: yon tan thams cad kyis mngon par mtho ba'i mkhan
NK013(pa)005:2233: chen lo ts+aa ba d+harma sh+r+ais bgyis pa'o //
NK013(pa)005:2234: 'dis rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che dar zhing rgyas la yun ring du gnas par gyur cig //
NK013(pa)005:2236: // sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhi ba'i sgrub pa'i thabs //
NK013(pa)005:2237: ngo mtshar cha shas gang ba'i ri bong can //
NK013(pa)005:2238: grangs med chu snod du mar gsal 'char ba /
NK013(pa)005:2239: smin grol kun gsal sgeg mo'i mkha' las so //
